OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,6,Fbright spells and occasional sunny
OL,7,Fintervals along with some showers,
OL,8,Fthese possibly on the heavy side in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,12,Fclear intervals and showers, these
OL,13,Fmore frequent over Argyll in the
OL,14,Fevening and early night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAnother mixed day with some
OL,17,Fbrighter spells but also some showers,
OL,18,Fthese becoming isolated later in the
OL,19,Fday. Lighter winds but a bit colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
